&lt;p&gt;Some of those are more striking than others. Like the four rapes, or the 59 stolen automobiles. Maybe the 3 assaults with deadly weapons. Or how about the nearly 300 noise complaints (in 90&amp;nbsp;days).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jeesh.&lt;/p&gt;
